<plot>When filmmaker Cullen Hoback travels to a private high school to make a movie, he scripts an alternate future for a real couple (both teachers) and their students. Quickly, the script reveals hidden truths in their lives, and the begins to transform all of the actors/real people involved. As lines get crossed, and reality blurs, the original film is never finished. What remains is part documentary, part fiction, in a one of a kind story that will keep you guessing long after the credits roll.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?204245</url></doc>
